// Tutorial is launched 15 seconds after first_login
#first-tutorial.modal.hide.fade
  .modal-header
    %button.close{"data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"} Ã—
    %h3 Welcome to Worth Reading
  .modal-body
    %p 
      To get started, start by adding some subscribers to your email list.
      = form_tag('/relationships', class: 'form-horizontal') do 
        %textarea.span4{ :name => "email_addresses",
                                          :size => "18", 
                                          :type => "text", 
                                          :placeholder => "Enter email addresses." }
        %button.btn.btn-primary{type: "submit"} Add Subscribers
      Afterwards, you can send a message to all of them by sending an email to
      subscribers@worth-reading.org.

    %p 
      Or you can just start by sending an email intended for johndoe@email.com to
      johndoe+email.com@worthreading.org.
  .modal-footer
    %a.btn{"data-dismiss" => "modal", :href => "#"} Close
